'''加瑪河'''（'''Jamma River'''）是[[青尼羅河|青尼羅河]]的右[[支流|支流]]，流域包括[[阿姆哈拉州|阿姆哈拉州]]和[[奧羅米亞州|奧羅米亞州]]，面積15,782平方公里.<ref>[http://www-wds.worldbank.org/external/default/WDSContentServer/WDSP/IB/2008/05/09/000334955_20080509032052/Rendered/PDF/434000PAD0P09617372B01off0use0only1.pdf "Tana & Beles Integrated Water Resources Development: Project Appraisal Document (PAD), Vol.1"] {{Wayback|url=http://www-wds.worldbank.org/external/default/WDSContentServer/WDSP/IB/2008/05/09/000334955_20080509032052/Rendered/PDF/434000PAD0P09617372B01off0use0only1.pdf |date=20160304193613 }}, World Bank, 2 May 2008 (accessed 5 May 2009)</ref>。上加瑪河流經陡峭的[[峽谷|峽谷]]、[[白堊紀|白堊紀]]時期形成的[[砂岩|砂岩]]和[[頁岩|頁岩]]。<ref name=NAI-web>[http://130.238.24.99/library/resources/dossiers/local_history_of_ethiopia/j/ORTJA.pdf "Local History in Ethiopia"] {{Wayback|url=http://130.238.24.99/library/resources/dossiers/local_history_of_ethiopia/j/ORTJA.pdf |date=20110528232445 }} (pdf) The Nordic Africa Institute website (accessed 29 January 2008)</ref>

加瑪河在十四世紀被首次提及<ref>G.W.B. Huntingford, ''The historical geography of Ethiopia from the first century AD to 1704'', (Oxford University Press: 1989), p. 69</ref>，[[傳教士|傳教士]]佩德羅·波埃茲（{{lang|pt|Pedro Páez}}）是首個[[歐洲人|歐洲人]]到訪和描述[[青尼羅河|青尼羅河]]的發源。


